---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="How decoded.finance collects and uses data.">
  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container max-w-4xl">
      <p class="label text-copper mb-2">Legal</p>
      <h1 class="mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6">Effective date: 20 February 2026</p>

      <div class="prose">
        <p>
          decoded.finance collects limited personal information that you choose to provide, such as your name, email
          address, and any details you share when subscribing to updates or interacting with the site.
        </p>
        <p>
          We use this information to deliver requested educational content, send occasional updates, maintain site
          security, and improve content quality and user experience.
        </p>
        <p>
          We process personal data on one or more of the following bases: your consent (for subscriptions and optional
          communications), our legitimate interests (operating and improving the website), and compliance with legal
          obligations where applicable.
        </p>
        <p>
          We may use third-party service providers to operate parts of the website, such as hosting and analytics.
          If additional processors are introduced, this policy will be updated accordingly.
        </p>
        <p>
          We retain personal data only for as long as reasonably necessary for the purposes described above, to meet
          legal obligations, and to resolve disputes. Access to submitted data is limited to authorized personnel.
        </p>
        <p>
          You may opt out of update emails at any time using the unsubscribe link. You may also request access,
          correction, or deletion of your personal data by reaching out via
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/abdulgaffarcfa/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn</a>.
        </p>
        <p>
          This website may contain links to third-party websites. We are not responsible for the privacy practices of
          external sites.
        </p>
        <p>
          We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Material updates will be reflected by revising the
          effective date on this page.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

